ATTRIBUTION NOTICE
------------------
Each record aggregates parameters from primary literature. The Harmonia dataset
records the curation, tier annotation, assay context, and inter-source
variability; it does NOT relicense the underlying primary measurements. When you
use a record, cite BOTH Harmonia AND the original source(s) named in the
record's `primary_citation` / `source_values` fields (each carries a DOI/PMID).

