SCOPE NOTICE
------------
The dataset is research / safety-methodology / education infrastructure. It is
NOT a regulatory safety determination and NOT a clinical tool. No record
constitutes a verdict that any drug is safe or unsafe. See README §Safety and
spec.md §10.
